DEST (Wizard Command)
=====================

Usage: dest <object>

Destruct (destroy) an object. The object will be completely removed from
the game.

Arguments:
  <object>  - The name of the object to destroy

Examples:
  dest sword          - Destroy the sword in your inventory or room
  dest rat            - Destroy the rat in the room
  dest sword 2        - Destroy the second sword

Notes:
  - Requires Wizard or higher access level
  - Be careful! Destructed objects cannot be recovered
  - Cannot destruct yourself or other players

See also: clone, load
